Titolo: Culpa Innata

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Culpa Innata (Latin: Original Sin or Innate Fault) is a third person point-and-click adventure game developed by Turkish company Momentum AS and published by Strategy First. The game invites the player into an exploration of a Utopian city of Adrianopolis through the eyes of Wallis, an officer who is investigating the murder of a citizen in a neighboring "Rogue State" in Odessa.